Package: MontyHall
Title: Monty Hall Problem and its Variants
Version: 1.1.1.1000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Nicholas",
           family = "Davis",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "nadavi13@asu.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package runs simulations based on the monty hall problem. The functions will perform a single
		simulation of the original problem, multiple simulations of the original problem, and the same with
		functions that will allow the user to define the amount of goats and cars in both a single observation
		and multiple.
